  {
    "client_msg_id": "2cd22e55-96e0-40d8-a145-949d67dc5467",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "It also got me thinking whether maths is an attempt to create de-metaphorized cognitive structures (but perhaps ends up just creating new metaphors to snap ideas into).",
